08.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Self-Esteem-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Self-Esteem-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Self-Esteem-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/self-esteem">Self Esteem</a>与 Meadowhall 合作推出限量版 T 恤，为乳腺癌慈善机构 Breast Cancer Now 筹集重要资金。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/self-esteem-cover-interview-2021-rebecca-taylor-prioritise-pleasure-3024342">自尊：“我想在我的议程中利用流行音乐的可口性来对付特洛伊木马”</a></strong></li></ul><p>该 T 恤的设计灵感源自 Self Esteem（真名 Rebecca Lucy Taylor）在 2022 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/tag/glastonbury">格拉斯顿伯里音乐节</a>舞台上所穿的 Meadowhall 圆顶风格服装，向谢菲尔德的购物和休闲目的地致敬，她分享了这一点从小就在她心中占有特殊的地位。</p><p>该服装是与格拉斯顿伯里原创服装的设计师 Ollie Spragley 合作设计的，Ollie Spragley 有自己的乳腺癌经历，今年是他母亲因病去世十周年。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C0OgeVIstEp/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg 