ync" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Marianne-Faithfull-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Marianne-Faithfull-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Marianne-Faithfull-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Marianne-Faithfull-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Marianne-Faithfull-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Marianne-Faithfull-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cat-power">Cat Power</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iggy-pop">Iggy Pop</a>在即将发行的向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/marianne-faithfull">Marianne Faithfull</a>致敬的专辑中翻唱了《Working Class Hero》。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/cat-power-covers-album-lana-del-rey-3150659">猫的力量：“吸引我的音乐要么是治愈，要么是放弃——两者择其一”</a></strong></li></ul><p>早在 11 月，就宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/iggy-pop-shirley-manson-and-more-to-appear-on-marianne-faithfull-covers-album-3536472">Faithfull 翻唱专辑正在制作中</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shirley-manson">雪莉·曼森 (Shirley Manson)</a>和桃子 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peaches">Peaches)</a>等人将在《Why D&#39;Ya Do It》中二重唱。</p><p>现在，Cat Power 和 Iggy Pop 联手翻唱了《Working Class Hero》，这首歌曲最初由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-lennon">John Lennon</a>创作，并由 Faithfull 在她的专辑《Broken English》（1979 年）中翻唱。</p><p>鲍尔在一份声明中谈到 Faithfull 时说道：“玛丽安过着美好的生活！！对于所有认识她和所有崇拜她的人来说，她都是女王！她对音乐世界的贡献是显而易见的！每次听到她华丽的歌声摇摆，我都会感动，我更接近永恒。在一个充满令人眼花缭乱的、新的、嘶嘶作响的歌曲和声音的世界里，玛丽安总是击中我的心灵和灵魂。我像其他人一样崇拜她。真正的贵妇，难以言表。永远的皇室。”</p><p>下面请听一下： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Cat Power 和 Iggy Pop - 工人阶级英雄（向 Marianne Faithfull 致敬）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/PZ57F7rB_kc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>到目前为止，The Parkington Sisters 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-breeders">The Breeders</a>的 Tanya Donelly 也分享了他们版本的 Faithfull 的《This Little Bird》。 “从童年到今天，玛丽安的声音一直是我最喜欢的乐器之一，她的音乐和精神一直是我一生的灵感，”唐纳利谈到封面时说道。</p><p> <strong>“The Faithful：向 Marianne Faithfull 致敬”曲目列表是：</strong><em><strong><br /></strong></em></p><p><strong>光盘1</strong><br /> <strong>01. 特雷西·博纳姆 – 《泪流满面》</strong><br /> <strong>02. Tanya Donelly &amp; The Parkington Sisters – &#39;This Little Bird&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>03. 乔西·科顿 – 《夏夜》</strong><br /> <strong>04.西尔维娅·布莱克——“吗啡姐妹”</strong><br /> <strong>05. Cat Power &amp; Iggy Pop – “工人阶级英雄”</strong><br /> <strong>06. 雪莉·曼森 (Shirley Manson) 和桃子 (Peaches) – &#39;Why D&#39;Ya Do It&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>07. Pom Poms – “人才流失”</strong><br /> <strong>08. Bush Tetras – &#39;内疚&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>09. 琼饰演女警察——“蹩脚英语”</strong><br /> <strong>10. Tammy Faye Starlite &amp; Barry Reynolds – “露西·乔丹之歌”</strong></p><p><strong>光盘二</strong><br /><strong>01. Honeychild Coleman – &#39;Over Here (No Time For Justice)&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>02. 阿黛尔·贝尔泰 – 《时代广场》</strong><br /> <strong>03. 妮可·阿特金斯 &amp; 吉姆·斯克拉武诺斯 – 《奇怪的天气》</strong><br /> <strong>04.莉迪亚午餐——“爱、生活和金钱”</strong><br /> <strong>05. Cynthia Ross（B Girls）和 Tim Bovaconti –“Vagabond Ways”</strong><br /> <strong>06. Donita Sparks – “靠魅力滑过人生”</strong><br /> <strong>07. 盖伊小姐 – &#39;与陌生人发生性关系&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>08. FaithNYC – &#39;Kissin&#39; Time&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>09. 女性侵略——“毒药之前”</strong></p><p>在 Faithfull 最近的其他新闻中，这位音乐家与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fka-twigs">FKA Twigs</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/denzel-curry">Denzel Curry</a>等人一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fka-twigs-denzel-curry-and-marianne-faithfull-join-musicians-for-palestine-pledge-3318163">签署了“音乐家支持巴勒斯坦”的承诺</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cat-power-and-iggy-pop-team-up-for-cover-of-john-lennons-working-clas